      "value": "<p>It is said this maneuver was once used to execute a guru of some repute. Make an attack. If it hits, it deals an additional 2d6 damage. The target must then make a Fortitude save (DC 14 + your initiation modifier) or become stunned for 1 round. If you have at least 12 initiator levels, you may instead make them paralyzed for 1 round. A creature that is sprouted takes a -4 penalty on their saving throw against this strike.</p>"
